prompt: Given the video of the blossoming tree in the garden where the person was performing a cartwheel, instantly transform the tree back into the young person in athletic clothes completing the cartwheel on the grass, with the garden environment unchanged.

Given the video of the lathe grooming a rotating mechanical insect limb, transform the limb instantly back into a solid rotating steel rod. The grooming claw changes back to a metal cutting tool, and all organic-mechanical features disappear.

Given the video of the young woman as a glowing neon cyber avatar against a magenta background, transform her figure back into a natural silhouette with soft side lighting, removing all neon lights and animated circuits while keeping the same pose and background.

Given the video of the historic Victorian hotel surrounded by palm trees on solid ground, transform the entire hotel and its surrounding palms into a floating island suspended in the sky.
